Drop pre-extracted dataset trees here for the assets image build to pick up.

Layout per dataset (one subdirectory per dataset key):

  reference-corpora-input/
    xview/
      <class>/*.png           (or labels.json + chips/<*.png>)
    dior/
      <class>/*.png
    hrsc2016/
      <class>/*.png
    shiprsimagenet/
      <class>/*.png

The fetcher at scripts/fetch_reference_datasets.py auto-detects these at
build time. Empty subdirectories (or a missing subdir entirely) cause the
adapter to log "skipped" without failing the build.

This directory is bind-mounted READ-ONLY into the asset image's build
context. Its contents are NEVER committed to git — see .gitignore.
